@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zkukhd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v1 = (tmp / (0.88 - tmp))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs(v2))
    v0 = (0.43 / wp.sin(0.95))
    v1 = 0.67
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v0 + 0.86 + v1 + 0.14)))
    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.60)) - wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.68)))
    tmp = (v2 * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.33) + (v1 + 0.83 + v0 + 0.10)))
    data[tid] = v0
